title._content: Mrs. Watson Homer at work on beaded buckskin gloves

description._content: Description/Notes: Photo shows Mrs. Watson Homer, of Toppenish, Washington, at work on beaded buckskin gloves in her tipi at Meadow Creek Indian Forest Camp. Photo was taken in the Gifford Pinchot National Forest. U.S. Forest Service photo #385219. Original Collection: Gerald W. Williams Collection Collection series: Native Americans album Item Number: WilliamsG:USFS385219 You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
